---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import DocsSidebar from "../../components/DocsSidebar.astro";
---
<Layout title="Rate limits · flipagent docs">
	<div class="cmw cmw-bordered">
		<div class="docs-shell">
			<DocsSidebar />
			<article class="docs-content">
				<h1>Rate limits</h1>
				<p class="lead">Per calendar month, UTC. Counted at every marketplace and value-add endpoint under <code>/v1/*</code>; management endpoints (<code>/v1/keys/*</code>, <code>/v1/billing/*</code>, <code>/v1/takedown</code>, <code>/healthz</code>) are uncounted.</p>

				<h2>Tier table</h2>
				<table class="api">
					<thead><tr><th>Tier</th><th>Calls / month</th><th>Notes</th></tr></thead>
					<tbody>
						<tr><td>Free</td><td>100</td><td>No card. <a href="/signup/">Sign up</a> for a key.</td></tr>
						<tr><td>Hobby ($19/mo)</td><td>5,000</td><td>Side projects, weekend builds.</td></tr>
						<tr><td>Pro ($99/mo)</td><td>50,000</td><td>Production integrations.</td></tr>
						<tr><td>Business</td><td>Custom</td><td>SLA, white-label, dedicated quota.</td></tr>
					</tbody>
				</table>

				<h2>What counts</h2>
				<p>Every request to a marketplace or intelligence endpoint counts toward your monthly quota: <code>/v1/buy/browse/*</code>, <code>/v1/buy/marketplace_insights/item_sales/*</code>, <code>/v1/buy/order/*</code>, <code>/v1/sell/inventory/*</code>, <code>/v1/sell/fulfillment/*</code>, <code>/v1/sell/finances/*</code>, <code>/v1/sell/account/*</code>, <code>/v1/commerce/*</code>, <code>/v1/post-order/*</code>, <code>/v1/evaluate</code>, <code>/v1/discover</code>, <code>/v1/research</code>, <code>/v1/match</code>, <code>/v1/ship/*</code>. Cache hits still count: the cache reduces latency, not your bill, because the infrastructure cost is the same regardless.</p>
				<p>Free routes (uncounted): <code>/v1/health/*</code>, <code>/v1/me/*</code>, <code>/v1/connect/*</code>, <code>/v1/billing/*</code>, <code>/v1/takedown</code>.</p>

				<h2>Headers on every authed response</h2>
				<div class="code"><pre><code>{`X-RateLimit-Limit:     100
X-RateLimit-Remaining: 73
X-RateLimit-Reset:     2026-05-01T00:00:00.000Z`}</code></pre></div>

				<h2>Hitting the limit</h2>
				<p>Once your counter reaches the tier limit, you'll get a <code>429</code> with the same headers and a JSON body:</p>
				<div class="code"><pre><code>{`{
  "error": "rate_limited",
  "message": "Tier \\"free\\" allows 100/mo; you've used 100.",
  "resetAt": "2026-05-01T00:00:00.000Z",
  "upgrade": "https://flipagent.dev/pricing"
}`}</code></pre></div>
				<p>The counter resets at <code>00:00 UTC</code> on the first of the next month. To raise the ceiling sooner, hit <code>POST /v1/billing/checkout</code> with <code>tier: "hobby"</code> or <code>"pro"</code>.</p>
			</article>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>
